Are you going to the military today?

496
00:39:42,531 --> 00:39:43,891
Will you meet General Su Dingfang?

497
00:39:45,091 --> 00:39:47,291
I have matters to attend to
and cannot disclose that,

498
00:39:48,091 --> 00:39:50,051
It is said that General Su has already arrived
outside the city,

499
00:39:50,051 --> 00:39:51,191
Take me to see him,

500
00:39:51,191 --> 00:39:52,551
I am most familiar with the roads here,

501
00:39:52,551 --> 00:39:53,971
I will certainly be able to lend him
a helping hand,

502
00:39:53,971 --> 00:39:55,611
May he soon annihilate that bandit Helu,

503
00:39:56,651 --> 00:39:57,728
Yunyi,

504
00:40:04,531 --> 00:40:06,331
Yunyi, don't be anxious,

505
00:40:07,251 --> 00:40:09,991
This time, 100,000 valiant troops of the Tang Dynasty
embarked on a campaign to the Western Regions,

506
00:40:09,991 --> 00:40:12,151
